">Answers to common questions from the fam</p></div></div></div><section class=\"py-16 md:py-24 px-4 container mx-auto\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"glass-light glass-shadow rounded-xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20\"><button class=\"w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left group\" aria-expanded=\"true\"><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-dark-brown group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">How long does shipping take?</span><span class=\"text-2xl text-primary transition-transform duration-300 rotate-45\">+</span></button><div style=\"height:0px;opacity:0\"><div class=\"px-6 pb-6 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed border-t border-black/5 pt-4\">We ship all ready-to-wear items within 1-3 business days. Domestic US shipping usually takes 3-5 days. For custom commissions, please allow 3-4 weeks for creation plus shipping time. If you need something for a specific festival date, please let us know in your order notes!</div></div></div><div class=\"glass-light glass-shadow rounded-xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20\"><button class=\"w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left group\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-dark-brown group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Do you ship internationally?</span><span class=\"text-2xl text-primary transition-transform duration-300 rotate-0\">+</span></button></div><div class=\"glass-light glass-shadow rounded-xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20\"><button class=\"w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left group\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-dark-brown group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">How do I care for my crochet pieces?</span><span class=\"text-2xl text-primary transition-transform duration-300 rotate-0\">+</span></button></div><div class=\"glass-light glass-shadow rounded-xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20\"><button class=\"w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left group\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-dark-brown group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">What is your return policy?</span><span class=\"text-2xl text-primary transition-transform duration-300 rotate-0\">+</span></button></div><div class=\"glass-light glass-shadow rounded-xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20\"><button class=\"w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left group\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-dark-brown group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Do you take custom commissions?</span><span class=\"text-2xl text-primary transition-transform duration-300 rotate-0\">+</span></button></div><div class=\"glass-light glass-shadow rounded-xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300 border border-white/20\"><button class=\"w-full px-6 py-5 flex items-center justify-between text-left group\" aria-expanded=\"false\"><span class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-dark-brown group-hover:text-primary transition-colors\">Are your materials sustainable?</span><span class=\"text-2xl text-primary transition-transform duration-300 rotate-0\">+</span></button></div></div><div class=\"mt-12 text-center p-8 bg-terracotta/5 rounded-2xl border border-terracotta/10\"><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-brown-warm mb-2\">Still relyin&#x27; on guessing?</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6\">If we didn&#x27;t answer your question, just shoot us a message.</p><a class=\"btn-primary inline-block\" href=\"/contact\">Contact Us</a></div></div></section></main></main><footer class=\"relative mt-20\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#2c1810] via-[#3d2e29] to-transparent opacity-90 -z-10\"></div><div class=\"glass-dark glass-shadow-xl border-t border-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-header font-bold text-primary\">Wookporium</h3><p class=\"text-warm-white/80 text-sm leading-relaxed\">Handcrafted festival apparel and natural jewelry for your journey, whatever that may be!</p><div class=\"flex gap-4 pt-2\"></div></div><div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-primary\">Shop</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-warm-white/80 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm\" href=\"/products\">All Products</a></li><li><a class=\"text-warm-white/80 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm\" href=\"/products?category=tops\">Tops</a></li><li><a class=\"text-warm-white/80 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm\" href=\"/products?category=bottoms\">Bottoms</a></li><li><a class=\"text-warm-white/80 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm\" href=\"/products?category=outerwear\">Outerwear</a></li><li><a class=\"text-warm-white/80 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm\" href=\"/products?category=headwear\">Headwear</a></li><li><a class=\"text-warm-white/80 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm\" href=\"/products?category=jewelry\">Jewelry</a></li><li><a class=\"text-warm-white/80 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm\" href=\"/products?category=accessories\">Accessories</a></li><li><a class=\"text-warm-white/80 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm\" href=\"/products?category=knick-knacks\">Knick-knacks</a></li></ul></div><div><h4 class=\"text-lg font-semibold mb-4 text-primary\">Info</h4><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-warm-white/80 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm\" href=\"/about\">About Us</a></li><li><a class=\"text-warm-white/80 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a></li><li><a class=\"text-warm-white/80 hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm\" href=