olicy?\",\"answer\":\"We accept returns on unworn, ready-to-wear items within 14 days of delivery. Custom commissions and sale items are final sale. Please verify your sizing before ordering custom pieces!\"},{\"question\":\"Do you take custom commissions?\",\"answer\":\"We open commission slots seasonally! Check our 'Contact' page to see if commissions are currently open. We love bringing your custom festival vision to life.\"},{\"question\":\"Are your materials sustainable?\",\"answer\":\"We strive to use natural, biodegradable fibers like cotton, bamboo, and hemp whenever possible. We also use upcycled embellishments for our one-of-a-kind pieces to minimize waste.\"}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-12 text-center p-8 bg-terracotta/5 rounded-2xl border border-terracotta/10\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-bold text-brown-warm mb-2\",\"children\":\"Still relyin' on guessing?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-gray-600 mb-6\",\"children\":\"If we didn't answer your question, just shoot us a message.\"}],[\"$\",\"$L9\",null,{\"href\":\"/contact\",\"className\":\"btn-primary inline-block\",\"children\":\"Contact Us\"}]]}]]}]}]]}],null,[\"$\",\"$La\",null,{\"children\":\"$Lb\"}]]}],{},null,false]},null,false]},null,false],[\"$\",\"$1\",\"h\",{\"children\":[null,[\"$\",\"$1\",\"JCyPLqCbqhcDBRlgvPgyX\",{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$Lc\",null,{\"children\":\"$Ld\"}],[\"$\",\"$Le\",null,{\"children\":\"$Lf\"}],null]}]]}],false]],\"m\":\"$undefined\",\"G\":[\"$10\",\"$undefined\"],\"s\":false,\"S\":true}\n6:[\"$\",\"footer\",null,{\"className\":\"relative mt-20\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#2c1810] via-[#3d2e29] to-transparent opacity-90 -z-10\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"glass-dark glass-shadow-xl border-t border-white/10 backdrop-blur-xl\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16\",\"children\":[\